Titles and abstracts of potential studies were assessed independently by three reviewers (AHX Yang, N. Kasabov, YO. Cakmak), according to the Preferred Reporting Items for Systematic Reviews and Meta-Analysis (PRISMA) guidelines [W4294215472]. The studies that met the inclusion and exclusion criteria were discussed and evaluated based on their content relative to the five research questions outlined above. Two reviewers (AHX Yang, YO. Cakmak) evaluated the full-text studies independently, while the third reviewer (N. Kasabov) resolved disagreements.

